            "text": "Search for the Decay of \u03b7 \u2192 3(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 )",
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "With the same data sample, the decay of \u03b7 \u2192 3(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 ) was searched for. ",
