            "paragraph_rank": 5,
            "section_rank": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "12 The mass spectrum of the 3(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 ) is shown in Fig. 1, where no events are observed in the \u03b7 mass region. ",
            "section": "Search for the Decay of \u03b7 \u2192 3(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 )",
            "paragraph_rank": 5,
            "section_rank": 4,
            "ref_spans": [
