        },
        {
            "text": "With the Feldman-Cousins frequentist approach, 13 the upper limit of the branching fraction is set to be B(\u03b7 \u2192 3(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 )) < 3.1 \u00d7 10 \u22125 at the 90% confidence level, where the systematic uncertainty is taken into account.",
